title: TW: Using Forever with TiddlyWiki
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

To keep the TiddlyWiki process running:

```
forever start --spinSleepTime 10000 /usr/local/bin/tiddlywiki /home/josh/apps/wiki/mywiki --listen "readers=(anon)" writers=josh username=YOURUSERNAME password=###########
```

To stop the TiddlyWiki process:

```
forever stop /usr/local/bin/tiddlywiki
```